26static unsigned int tree_merge_probs_impl(unsigned int i,
27 const vpx_tree_index *tree,
28 const vpx_prob *pre_probs,
29 const unsigned int *counts,
30 vpx_prob *probs) {
31 const int l = tree[i];
32 const unsigned int left_count =
33 (l <= 0) ? counts[-l]
34 : tree_merge_probs_impl(l, tree, pre_probs, counts, probs);
35 const int r = tree[i + 1];
36 const unsigned int right_count =
37 (r <= 0) ? counts[-r]
38 : tree_merge_probs_impl(r, tree, pre_probs, counts, probs);
39 const unsigned int ct[2] = { left_count, right_count };
40 probs[i >> 1] = mode_mv_merge_probs(pre_probs[i >> 1], ct);
41 return left_count + right_count;
42}
43
44void vpx_tree_merge_probs(const vpx_tree_index *tree, const vpx_prob *pre_probs,
45 const unsigned int *counts, vpx_prob *probs) {
46 tree_merge_probs_impl(0, tree, pre_probs, counts, probs);
47}
